name: Jupiter
reason: The King of Aggregators. Incredible product, but the token is 50% team/reserve controlled. High central planning risk.

name: Sanctum
reason: Infrastructure for launching new LSTs. Solves the liquidity fragmentation problem. Innovative utility.

name: Meteora
reason: Dynamic Liquidity Market Maker. Optimizes capital efficiency for LPs. Real engineering value.

name: Streamflow
reason: The 'ADP' of Solana. Handles payroll and token vesting. Essential tool for enforcing honesty in other projects.

name: Bonfida
reason: Solana Name Service (.sol). Pure utility protocol for identity. Moderate tariff due to old-school heavy vesting.

name: Solanium
reason: Legacy launchpad. Charges rent to launch other tokens. Minimal technical innovation in recent years.

name: 1inch (Wormhole)
reason: Competitor aggregator. Good utility, but token is pure governance/rent-seeking.

name: Less Fn Gas
reason: Attempts to solve gas fees via tokenomics. High 'Vibes', low technical structural change.
